dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading.; Shows township and range, county boundaries, land district boundaries, towns, railroads, water features, and areas containing coal. Also shows Indian, military and forest reservations.; Prime meridians: Greenwich (top) and Washington, D.C. (bottom).; At head of title: Department of the Interior, General Land Office, William A. Richards, Commissioner.; Dec. 19 1906 and S Doc 194 59 2-- lower right margin.; Insets: Evanston -- Laramie -- Sheriden and vicinity -- Cheyenne and vicinity.
